-- China Billionaire Li Jinyuan to Visit Colombia, Portafolio Says
-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r i s t o w
-- 2012-07-11T15:54:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-11/china-billionaire-li-jinyuan-to-visit-colombia-portafolio-says.html
Chinese billionaire Li Jinyuan will
travel to Colombia this week to discuss a mining project with
President  Juan Manuel Santos  and other officials, Portafolio
 reported , without saying where it obtained the information.  Li, chairman and chief executive officer of Tiens Biotech
Group USA Inc., will be in Colombia July 14-18, the Bogota-based
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Matthew Bristow in Bogota at 
 mbristow5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Goodman at 
 jgoodman19@bloomberg.net  